11/14.(Sun.)5 Common types of water leakages and solutions/21 Tiny Inconveniences That Actually Drive You Crazy (William)<br /><br />This is online meeting. <br />加入 Zoom 會議<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... NKSU5MQT09<br /><br />會議 ID：929 8726 6213<br />密碼：112233<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Presentation 1<br />8:00-8:10 pm Break<br />8:10-8:40: Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation 2<br /><br />At the presentation, the time limit is 1-2 minutes for each speaker.<br /><br />Article1:<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://sghomeneeds.com/articles/water-leakages-and-solution">https://sghomeneeds.com/articles/water- ... d-solution</a><!-- m --><br /><br />5 Common types of water leakages and solutions<br /><br />1. Have you ever experienced a drip water coming from the ceiling above you ? Has the leakage been fixed ? Who will pay the repair expense ?<br />2. How do you find the competent contractor and plumber to repair the leakage ?<br />3. Have you ever used DIY to repair the leakages ? Was it difficult ?<br />4. If you want to buy a house. How do you choose the good construction building ?<br /><br />Article2:<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.buzzfeed.com/stephenlaconte/little-things-that-make-people-rage">https://www.buzzfeed.com/stephenlaconte ... eople-rage</a><!-- m --><br /><br />What are the little things in day life that drive you crazy ?<br />What annoys you the most in the following :<br /><br />1. Making loud personal call in your office.<br />2. This woman put her bare feet on the back of this man's chair.<br />3. Drivers who don't signal when changing lanes. It takes a second.<br />4. When two people in a store stop, carts side by side, and block the entire aisle to have a conversation.<br />5. The lavatory has a sign to indicate that it's occupied . There are always people trying to open the door just to make sure that it's really in use.<br /><br />----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Thu Nov 11, 2021 4:39 pm</p><hr />
